Text: Awesome stuff as always man. Anyway to get a Children 18:3 discography? Thanks if you can!

Lingerdog, all done.  It's up and active for you right now.  And I do believe it's a complete discography of the following five albums:  2004 - Places I Don't Want To Go, 2006 - Songs Of Desperation, 2008 - Children 18-3, 2010 - Rain's A Comin, and 2012 - On The Run.  Enjoy!  :)
